      ],
      "suggestion": "Introduce a shared error-handling policy abstraction (for example: required/optional/best-effort with explicit typed outcomes) and require each operation to declare its policy. Route all major workflows through it so degradations are explicit (status/result object) rather than ad-hoc log-and-continue branches.",
